-- Time Warner, KKR, TPG on Dogan Yayin sale short list: sources
-- 
-- Wed Jan 5, 2011 3:10am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/01/05/us-dogan-idUSTRE70416C20110105

 

 ISTANBUL  (Reuters) - Time Warner ( TWX.N ), KKR ( KKR.N ) and TPG are on the short list of potential buyers of assets belonging to Dogan Yayin ( DYHOL.IS ), Turkey's biggest media group, sources familiar with the deal said on Wednesday. 

 Hurriyet newspaper, Dogan Yayin's biggest-selling daily, is not in the current group of assets for sale, the sources said. The starting price for the properties on sale is seen starting at $1.6 billion and $1.8 billion, according to the sources. None of the companies, including Dogan Yayin, were available for immediate comment. (Reporting by Seda Sezer and Birsen Altayli)